-speaking world (usually pronounced ‘<b>loo</b>-ee’). In Britain the Anglicized form   Lewis   is rather more common, whereas in America the reverse is true."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Ludwig VON TÜBINGEN was born about 1118, his father, Palatine Count Hugo von Tübingen III, was 28 and his mother, Hemma von Zollern, was 23. He had at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"um 1118–":"umbes 1118–Surnud","1115–1182":"1115–1182","1118–1167":"1118–1167","1118–Male":"1118–Surnud","1120–1167":"1120–1167","1120–Female":"1120–Surnud","1125–1182":"1125–1182","–1162":"–1162","1140–1169":"1140–1169","1091–1152":"1091–1152","1097–1152":"1097–1152","1091":"1091","1120":"1120","1097":"1097","1152":"1152","1140":"1140","1162":"1162","1182":"1182","1118":"1118","1115":"1115","1169":"1169","1125":"1125","1167":"1167","um 1118":"umbes 1118"},"fi":{"um 1118–":"noin 1118–Kuollut","1115–1182":"1115–1182","1118–1167":"1118–1167","1118–Male":"1118–Kuollut","1120–1167":"1120–1167","1120–Female":"1120–Kuollut","1125–1182":"1125–1182","–1162":"–1162","1140–1169":"1140–1169","1091–1152":"1091–1152","1097–1152":"1097–1152","1091":"1091","1120":"1120","1097":"1097","1152":"1152","1140":"1140","1162":"1162","1182":"1182","1118":"1118","1115":"1115","1169":"1169","1125":"1125","1167":"1167","um 1118":"noin 1118"},"fr":{"um 1118–":"environ 1118–Décédé","1115–1182":"1115–1182","1118–1167":"1118–1167","1118–Male":"1118–Décédé","1120–1167":"1120–1167","1120–Female":"1120–Décédée","1125–1182":"1125–1182","–1162":"–1162","1140–1169":"1140–1169","1091–1152":"1091–1152","1097–1152":"1097–1152","1091":"1091","1120":"1120","1097":"1097","1152":"1152","1140":"1140","1162":"1162","1182":"1182","1118":"1118","1115":"1115","1169":"1169","1125":"1125","1167":"1167","um 1118":"environ 1118","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Ludwig VON TÜBINGEN est né environ 1118, son père, Palatine Count Hugo von Tübingen III, avait 28 ans et sa mère, Hemma von Zollern, avait 23 ans. Il a eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"um 1118–":"um 1118–Verstorben","11